    "In this setting, training and validation datasets were merged, and a model was trained using integrated datasets.",
    "After the training steps, the trained model with integrated training datasets was evaluated on individual test datasets.",
    "For example, to test the BIOSNAP test dataset, the model was first trained using DAVIS, Binding DB, and BIOSNAP's training datasets, and then tested on BIOSNAP's test dataset.",
    "Generally, the diversity and quantity of datasets are linked to the improvement of prediction performance.",
    "Therefore, we also assessed the impact of dataset integrations using DLM-DTI."
